Challenges Encountered

During development several technical challenges were addressed:

JSON Output Instability
Local LLM responses sometimes returned malformed JSON.
Solution:
implemented regex cleaning
enforced strict output formats

Model Latency
Large prompts increased response times.
Solution:
optimized prompts
simplified agent instructions

Cost Estimation Issues
Machine outputs initially returned descriptions rather than models.
Solution:
standardized machine catalog
mapped machines to pricing database

OpenAI Dependency Errors
LlamaIndex attempted to use OpenAI embeddings.
Solution:
switched to local embedding models